content: Heading back to NYC from Japan. Bittersweet, but my sketchbook's full of inspiration and my heart's ready for what's next. 🇯🇵✨
raw_content: Excited yet bittersweet to be heading back to NYC from Japan. The experience here has fueled my creativity and opened my eyes in ways I'll carry with me. What will I bring back? A sketchbook full of inspiration and a heart eager for what's next. 🇯🇵✨ #NYCbound
